EXIF to DC normaliser v1.0-FINAL
A SPRUSH MASHUP TOOL - SUPPORTING THE DIGITAL PRESERVATION COMMUNITY
http://wiki.opf-labs.org/display/SPR/Home

Author: Maurice de Rooij, Dutch National Archives, september 2012
License: APACHE2

Usage:
       exif_to_dc.php file=FILENAME
       exif_to_dc.php folder=FOLDERNAME ; (NOTE: recursive!)
Optionally, specify an XML output file:
       exif_to_dc.php file=FILENAME|folder=FOLDERNAME xmlout=FILE.xml
otherwise it will print XML to STDOUT

Background:
This tool enables you to read EXIF data from an image file using EXIFTOOL 
and normalise this to Dublin Core compatible XML adding specific metadata 
contained in an .ini file. The XML output templates can be tailored to one's needs.
More information:
http://wiki.opf-labs.org/display/SPR/Maintain+a+list+of+metadata+mappings+outside+of+the+script
